Patch,is,a,community,specific,news,and,information,platform,that,aims,to,provide,local,coverage,for,individual,towns,and,communities,The,Patch,API,lets,developers,integrate,the,same,hyperlocal,content,into,their,sites,and,applications,The,API,accepts,location,based,information,of,U,S,neighborhoods,ZIP,codes,cities,or,states,into,their,Stories,Query,Resource,and,returns,locally,relevant,aggregated,content,from,over,other,sources,in,JSON,format